spanGrp.span: Yís të sũã' pe jũ yu-lë rö bá
I saw that there were logs standing; there were logs;
Yís sũã' kalwögichi dujali inga Kalwögichi dujali
they pulled their heads, drank water and hid.
tsagu sigö-gẽ diglö ye-gẽ-ite í ña blö-gẽ
Yís sũã' (_) bá rama í rö [incompr]
I see that it was nice.
Je rö bá rama yís sũẽ rö
I liked the house; it was nicely built.
S-wöbötsá-wã pe jũ-wa pe jũ (_) yu-lë rö bá
But there was nice water there; that’s what I saw.
taranã bá diglö diglö tsõ í ska Je sũã' yís je sũã' yís të
I saw it in that computer.
Tebeli yaga is this, where one can see. It is called tebeli yaga.
Tebeli_yaga es esto que uno (m) (_) uno lo ve Se llama se llama tebeli yaga
In there I saw everything was very nice.
Je nã je nã yís të í sũã' (_) köũ bá rama
Person here/person like/the person sitting here shows us that.
Pe jiska/ pe bi/ pe kajkirinã je të kashe-gẽ sa ĩã
